  <Docs>
    <summary>Defines the reader, writer, and methods for pre-generated, typed serializers.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 To improve the performance of XML serialization, you can generate assemblies before serialization using the [XML Serializer Generator Tool (Sgen.exe)](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md). When such an assembly is loaded, the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer> uses the properties of the XmlSerializerImplementation interface to query the contained serializer or serializers.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
